Component.Description:
Grabbable is a component that allows an object to be grabbed by a controller. It requires the
Mesh Component to be present.

@param enabled Defines whether the object can be grabbed or not.
@param type The type of behavior an object has when grabbed (faces user, pivots on y axis, etc.)
@param isGrabbed Whether the object is currently grabbed or not
@param minHeight the minimum height an object can be held when grabbed
@param maxHeight the maximum height an object can be held when grabbed
